" No scrollbars
set noscrollbars

" Scroll 4 times as fast
noremap j 4j
noremap k 4k

" Incremental search
set incsearch

" Focus content, instead of input after loading site
set focuscontent

" Open messenger sidebar with s and close with S
map s :sidebar Messenger for Facebookâ„¢<CR>
map S :sbclose<CR>

" Select all in input field
inoremap <C-a> <C-Home><C-S-End>

" Open picture location with C-c p
map <C-c>p ;i

" Open context menu with C-c m
map <C-c>m ;c

" Tab traversal
map J <C-p>
map K <C-n>

" Search in bookmarks
map B :bmarks<SPACE>

" Search in tabs
map T :buffer<SPACE>
